# Luxanvoryx Design Guidelines

## Color Palette
- **Primary Colors**:
  - Cosmic Black (#000000)
  - Deep Space (#0a0a1f)
  - Nebula Purple (#2a0a3a)
- **Accent Colors**:
  - Electric Blue (#00e5ff)
  - Hologram Purple (#b967ff)

## Typography
- Use system fonts (no custom fonts needed)
- Font family: 'harmony' [-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, etc.]
- For monospace elements: Use system monospace

## UI Elements
- Use gradient backgrounds for cards and buttons
- Apply subtle glow effects to important UI elements
- Implement micro-animations for interactive elements
- Maintain high contrast between text and backgrounds
- Use rounded corners (borderRadius: 24.0) for cards and containers

## Layout
- Implement proper spacing and alignment
- Use card-based designs for content grouping
- Ensure responsive layouts that work on different screen sizes

## Navigation
- Bottom navigation with 3 main sections
- Floating action button for primary actions
- Use clear visual feedback for interactive elements
